CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 24, 1956, page 26, reads: "Getting Ready - Members of the Centre Ave. YMCA Big Five basketball team are busily preparing for the 1956-57 season. The Big Five is expected to floor one of its strongest aggregations in several seasons. They will play in County Basketball League. Players show above are, left to right, Rudy Riley, George Brown, Delton Heard, Donald Meyers, player-coach; Craig Copeland, Neal Humphrey and Pate Wade. Players not shown are Charlie Cooper, Bobby Jones, William Strothers, James Covington and James Branch. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait Centre Avenue YMCA basketball players, including left to right: #24 Rudy Riley, #13 George Brown, #23 Delton Heard, coach Donald Meyers holding basketball, #33 Craig Copeland, #11 Neal Humphrey, and #14 Pate Wade, standing in gymnasium, seen from above
